Text: SEED and ENJOY by T.F.K team
GAME CRASHES EVERY TIME U FINISH IN 1ST PLACE ANY SOLUTIONS?

Ok, smart arse remarks aside, since it's a cutscene issue, your AV might be stopping the player from launching; check your AV for last known issues and allow the player, or game exe into your trusted files, it might be that the AV simply doesn't know the player or codec so by default goes into sus mode shutting the launcher down, can't hurt to check it out.
